snippet: Jeff Fisher thought receiver Brian Quick got both feet down on a sideline catch in the third quarter, but the Los Angeles Rams coach couldn't find the red challenge flag in the bulky parka he was wearing on a chilly day in New England....
lead_paragraph: Jeff Fisher thought receiver Brian Quick got both feet down on a sideline catch in the third quarter, but the Los Angeles Rams coach couldn't find the red challenge flag in the bulky parka he was wearing on a chilly day in New England.

headline.main: Rams Give Fisher, Snead Contract Extensions
